    "IntroductionDecentralized Finance or \"DeFi\" is the latest Fintech trend [1] that takes the world of Finance by storm [2].",
    "Owing to its decentralized nature, it juxtaposes traditional finance [3] or centralized finance, also referred to as TradFi and CeFi, respectively [4,5].",
    "Owing to its combinatory possibilities, some authors have referred to it as \"Money Lego\" [6] or the \"Lego of Finance\" [7].",
    "However, what exactly is in the box of financial click bricks?",
    "What precisely constitutes DeFi, and what can be built from it?"
